aveimdir(prefix)

Procedure for Igor Pro software. calculate average image from all images named starting with same prefix in a given data folder.
By Alex Tran-Van-Minh (alexandra.tran.van.minh@gmail.com)


INSTALLATION: 

copy avesamedir.ipf file in the Igor Procedure subfolder in your Wavemetrics folder. Restart Igor Pro

////

As argument the user enters the prefix of the images to average 
By example typing in command window aveimdir("image") will create and display an average of all 2d waves which name starts with "image"
in the current data folder
